    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Hockey Insider Dislikes Fighting</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor</p>
        <p>I grew up in a family with Rangers season tickets and began playing hockey at age 4. I still play hockey four times a week at age 42. I share this information only to establish my credentials as an insider, as opposed to the outsiders who, Anaheim General Manager Brian Burke said, always start the debate about fighting in hockey. But I hate fighting in hockey.</p>
        <p>Seth Kim-Cohen  New Haven</p>
      </block>
